code: @Override public void notifyPartitionConsumable(JobID jobId, ResultPartitionID partitionId, final TaskActions taskActions) {     CompletableFuture<Acknowledge> acknowledgeFuture = jobMasterGateway.scheduleOrUpdateConsumers(partitionId, timeout).     acknowledgeFuture.whenCompleteAsync((Acknowledge ack, Throwable throwable) -> {         if (throwable != null) {             LOG.error("Could not schedule or update consumers at the JobManager.", throwable).             taskActions.failExternally(new RuntimeException("Could not notify JobManager to schedule or update consumers.", throwable)).         }     }, executor). }
